      <title>五角大楼几天后表示，国防部长奥斯汀住院</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/defense-secretary-lloyd-austin-hospitalized-over-complication</link>
      <description><![CDATA[五角大楼周五晚上表示，美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀因“最近一次选择性医疗手术后出现并发症”而住院。他入院四天后，没有提供进一步的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/defense-secretary-lloyd-austin-hospitalized-over-complication</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 01:22:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登和特朗普继续攻击选票问题，给竞选蒙上阴影</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/biden-trump-go-on-attack-with-ballot-question-clouding-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院宣布将审理一个影响美国总统选举进程核心的案件，前总统唐纳德·特朗普和总统乔·拜登周五在决斗演讲中展开对决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-06/biden-trump-go-on-attack-with-ballot-question-clouding-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Jan 2024 00:26:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿克曼在妻子被指控后希望麻省理工学院教师进行抄袭检查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/ackman-wants-plagiarism-checks-on-mit-faculty-after-wife-accused</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·阿克曼 (Bill Ackman) 周五表示，在他的妻子内里·奥克斯曼 (Neri Oxman) 被指控在没有引用的情况下抄袭麻省理工学院论文的某些段落后，他将开始检查麻省理工学院所有现任教员的抄袭行为。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/ackman-wants-plagiarism-checks-on-mit-faculty-after-wife-accused</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 23:27:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自#MeToo以来，女性对经济学的满意度有所下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/satisfaction-among-women-in-economics-has-fallen-since-metoo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新的调查显示，与五年前相比，2023 年对经济学专业环境感到满意的女性人数有所减少，尽管在此期间为改善女性在该领域的条件做出了努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/satisfaction-among-women-in-economics-has-fallen-since-metoo</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 23:22:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>警方使用的谷歌搜索技术引发新的法律挑战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/google-search-technique-used-by-police-draws-new-legal-challenge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[公民自由倡导者对警方使用谷歌搜索数据帮助解决刑事案件提出了新的挑战，因为这种做法在全国范围内受到了更严格的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/google-search-technique-used-by-police-draws-new-legal-challenge</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 23:18:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>紧急堕胎纠纷接受美国最高法院审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/emergency-abortion-dispute-gets-review-by-us-supreme-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院同意考虑医院是否可以在紧急情况下进行堕胎，即使是在几乎完全禁止堕胎的州。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/emergency-abortion-dispute-gets-review-by-us-supreme-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 22:12:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院同意听取特朗普科罗拉多州选票上诉</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/supreme-court-agrees-to-hear-trump-colorado-ballot-appeal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院同意考虑科罗拉多州是否可以禁止唐纳德·特朗普参加总统选举，处理因他试图推翻 2020 年选举而引发的具有里程碑意义的宪法和政治冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/supreme-court-agrees-to-hear-trump-colorado-ballot-appeal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 22:02:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登在反对特朗普时称选票上是民主</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-casts-trump-threat-to-democracy-as-central-to-2024-race</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登拉开了今年的首次竞选活动，他直截了当地向选民表明，他的前任唐纳德·特朗普是民主的威胁，不应该重返白宫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/biden-casts-trump-threat-to-democracy-as-central-to-2024-race</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 19:43:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>州政府辩称，特朗普因欺诈欠纽约人 3.7 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州告诉一位法官，最终将对民事欺诈案作出判决，唐纳德·特朗普及其公司应被责令支付 3.7 亿美元，高于 2.5 亿美元，因为十多年来在财务记录中夸大了他的资产价值审判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/new-york-now-seeks-370-million-from-trump-in-civil-fraud-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 17:27:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>朝鲜可能向俄罗斯发送最新导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/north-korea-appears-to-be-sending-its-newest-missiles-to-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国指责朝鲜向俄罗斯发射的导弹似乎来自其最新的核火箭系列，这些火箭易于隐藏、部署迅速且难以击落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-05/north-korea-appears-to-be-sending-its-newest-missiles-to-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Jan 2024 12:08:30 GMT</pubDate>
